OL,3,CHistoric department store being
OL,4,Cbrought back to life in Bath
OL,6,FITV News spoke to those behind the
OL,7,Fproject to bring Jolly's back to its
OL,8,Fformer glory.
OL,10,FAn historic department store in Bath
OL,11,Fwhich closed last month after trading
OL,12,Ffor more than 200 years will reopen
OL,13,Fnext year.
OL,15,FJolly's on Milsom Street is being
OL,16,Ftaken on by London-based chain Morley
OL,17,FStores Ltd, which plans to reopen the
OL,18,Fsite in Spring 2026.
