OL,3,CHistoric department store being
OL,4,Cbrought back to life in Bath
OL,6,FCouncillor Kevin Guy, Bath and North
OL,7,FEast Somerset Council leader, said:
OL,8,F"Morleys Stores will bring an exciting
OL,9,Fshopping experience to residents and
OL,10,Fvisitors alike and I am delighted to
OL,11,Fwelcome the business to our vibrant
OL,12,Fcity and to one of the most loved
OL,13,Fstores in Bath.
OL,15,F"Milsom Street has always been a very
OL,16,Fspecial shopping destination and
OL,17,FMorleys Stores is a fantastic fit for
OL,18,Fthe area.
