OL,6,F"Morleys' decision complements the
OL,7,Finvestment the council is making in
OL,8,Fthe Milsom Quarter.
OL,10,F"The council has been working hard
OL,11,Fover the past 18 months to secure the
OL,12,Ffuture of this flagship store and a
OL,13,Fsignificant element of the plan is to
OL,14,Fmake it once again the anchor store
OL,15,Ffor Milsom Street."
