OL,6,FCouncillor Mark Elliott, cabinet
OL,7,Fmember for Resources, added: "We set
OL,8,Fout the council's commitment to the
OL,9,Flocal economy in our ten-year Economic
OL,10,FStrategy and this investment is a very
OL,11,Fpositive recognition of the great
OL,12,Fretail offer our city has and the work
OL,13,Fthe council has undertaken to support
OL,14,Fit. I join others in welcoming Morleys
OL,15,FStores to Bath."
