OL,6,FAllan Winstanley, chief executive of
OL,7,FMorleys Department Stores, said: "We
OL,8,Fare thrilled to start preparations to
OL,9,Fopen up in Jolly's and restore this
OL,10,Fheritage store to its former glory for
OL,11,FBath.
OL,13,F"Our business treats all our stores as
OL,14,Funique independent stores, designed to
OL,15,Fserve their local community with
OL,16,Fcurated and considered product
OL,17,Fcollections and store experiences.
